{"tid":205570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（自由行拜拜）九展E-max 變身Outlet 「做返九成本地客生意」","createTime":"2017-04-18T01:12:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T11:47:14.000Z","uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e546e9468ce847d1a5bd039334221ea3275e3d1","tid":205570,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:12:58.000Z","msg":"合和（054）資產管理有限公司董事梁庇世指，旗下九龍灣國際展貿中心商場E-max因應自由行旅客銳減，去年把近萬呎面積轉做散貨場，10月起更正式搞品牌Outlet（特賣場），希望藉此吸家庭客，「做返九成本地客生意」。<br />\n<br />\nE-max於 2007年完成翻新工程，正值自由行風光之時，梁庇世感嘆：<span style=\"color: red;\">「以前我地高峰時，一日有100架旅遊巴喺門口，但最近幾個月只得10至20架。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nE-max第一期Outlet已營運近半年，&hellip;&hellip;以中檔為主，如Gap、Folli Follie、Cotton On等。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;E-max正改劃近12萬呎、原本屬名車展的地方，作擴充第二期，料明年暑假開業。"},{"pid":"8cfeed1e2f3f23167832936e358ba54548693cc8","tid":205570,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:15:24.000Z","msg":"講真去emax都係睇戲<br />\n個outlet又細又唔好行"},{"pid":"9a5bde003d73a6fe5ea84936eb7d9187fa809d26","tid":205570,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:20:49.000Z","msg":"咩叫做「返」, 唔係睇show睇戲既有撚本地客專登黎?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0052737b30b6bbf2697b2a385e90994a0c308de8","tid":205570,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:22:54.000Z","msg":"我去emax貪佢睇戲泊車優惠唔係都唔會去"},{"pid":"64b773b8266370033df941aada27556cfe7b76d7","tid":205570,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:26:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7ac1e6cf02f85a794297fe70d65c6c88c759ec2","tid":205570,"uid":21283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T01:29:25.000Z","msg":"新開條食街幾間都麻麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa26ac6363f690da78aa4b57be5e31b422df2a3","tid":205570,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0